 popular incumbent mayor chen shui bian during his visit to silicon valley mayor ma focused on taipei's role in global high technology industries and met with university and high technology company leaders taipei's changing role in global it industries search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest documentary looks at media coverage of nixon's visit to china january 10 2012 shorenstein aparc announcement us visit to myanmar a major step shorenstein aparc seaf in the news international business times on december 2 2011 shorenstein aparc scholars provide essential insight into obama asia visit november 10 2010 shorenstein aparc in the news kim jong il visit to china tests south korean leadership korea times on may 6 2010 siegfried hecker's report on north korea visit to senate foreign relations committee march 25 2008 cisac fsi stanford news president of latvia visit is cancelled march 25 2005 news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
